1. Create twitter account 'weater_<yourname>'
2. Go to apps.twitter.com while logged in to new account.
2a. New application. Website URL is not important. Callback URL leave empty.
2b. Create access token
3. Install 'nvm' from https://github.com/creationix/nvm
4. Run 'nvm install stable'
5. Create directory, run 'npm init'
5a. Fill out details. Leave things blank if unsure.
6. Now you have package.json
7. Install twitter NPM package: npm install --save twitter
8. Go to https://github.com/joostlubach/weather-joost for examples.